From: Harmen Stoppels <harmen@stoppels.ch>
Date: Tue, 2 Jun 2026 07:31:39 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] 0002: libiberty/strsignal.c const-qualify psignal message arg

Match musl's psignal prototype (const char *).
---
 libiberty/strsignal.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/libiberty/strsignal.c b/libiberty/strsignal.c
index 666b1b4f1..2f6070230 100644
--- a/libiberty/strsignal.c
+++ b/libiberty/strsignal.c
@@ -551,7 +551,7 @@ followed by a newline.
 #ifndef HAVE_PSIGNAL
 
 void
-psignal (int signo, char *message)
+psignal (int signo, const char *message)
 {
   if (signal_names == NULL)
     {
